Base API
BASE_URL = https://yourdomain.com/api
Use authentication header:
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKENAccept: application/jsonContent-Type: application/json

1. Auth APIs
POST   /auth/loginPOST   /auth/logoutGET    /auth/mePOST   /auth/forgot-passwordPOST   /auth/reset-passwordPOST   /auth/change-password
Login Payload
{  "email": "admin@example.com",  "password": "password123"}

