3. Franchise Admin APIs
Prefix:
/api/franchise
Middleware:
auth:sanctumrole:franchise_admin
Important rule:
Every franchise API must use logged_in_franchise_id.Franchise admin should not pass franchise_id manually for security.Backend should get franchise_id from authenticated user.

